Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.70,0:01:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(宿命之巧遇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回來了，到底如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辦理停留的手續十分煩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.71,0:02:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在逼我們離開似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.05,0:02:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.05,0:02:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們仍未接到\N帝姆艦隊命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且外面還有敵軍駐守！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅什麼時候回來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.99,0:02:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大約2個小時左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很重要的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，他說是非常重要的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.86,0:02:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，吩咐他們\N3小時內做好整備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.73,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨時出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.68,0:02:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀...早知看看\N天氣預測表才出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠真可憐呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.37,0:04:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...對不起\N我不是存心嚇妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是說這天鵝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳很喜歡牠嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上那有人\N不喜歡美麗的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上那有人\N不喜歡美麗的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.99,0:04:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上那有人\N不喜歡美麗的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人不喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上那有人\N不喜歡美麗事物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到美麗的東西衰老死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會難過的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然會的！是的，小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想請教你一件事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨停了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.35,0:05:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的眼睛長得很神氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.49,0:05:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以不理會\N康斯肯的部隊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.56,0:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時再算吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德茲爾中將和康斯肯都是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是看眼前的敵人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希莉亞少將卻不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她能夠看透\N整個戰局的發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有甚麼事\N要在衛星六號內辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經很快接近這大戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時你便會知道的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們駛入港口吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞上校的贊斯巴爾\N正在駛入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星六號的港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.36,0:06:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞？這傢伙\N每次都是胡來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.98,0:06:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界的發展\N真今人意想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然會和敵軍\N停在同一個港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有在中立衛星內\N才可辦到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做戲！\N簡直如做戲一樣呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如我們\N請吉翁的人一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開派對還好呢！\N說得沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我忍耐不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是去報仇了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.01,0:07:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死良的敵人\N就在眼前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准人，如果在衛星內開戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.51,0:07:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會怎樣，你知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會不知道吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.58,0:07:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就快要離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.52,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要禁止所有人擅自出入\N明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦內應還有\N很多工作尚未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻回去自己的崗位吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你們\N別再更改停留時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有武器的封條...\N我知怎做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你們別再和聯邦軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有任何爭執的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經交待清楚\N辛苦你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？你能夠\N成為鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我便開心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.35,0:07:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚交給你零件怎樣？\N咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.36,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的發明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了它\N會有絕大的效果的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的有用？那我成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要繼續再研究\N研究些新發明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.65,0:08:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有用\N我做出來的當然有用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.56,0:09:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種防空洞\N對空襲是沒用的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.99,0:09:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸你認為機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比人命更重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快搬鋼彈上去！   爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也快上去白色基地吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.27,0:09:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，動不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.32,0:09:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知這樣就不走這邊了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.15,0:10:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.56,0:10:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這位朋友的技術不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我還以為可以避得過！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看要用車拉才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫什麼名？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，我叫阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.38,0:10:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅？我好像聽過的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.85,0:10:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞\N我知道你便是夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我來幫手好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了，我自己可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N請問閣下尊姓大名？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.37,0:10:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞‧阿茲納布爾\N你看得出來吧，我是個軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉！妳試試開動它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.75,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記著要慢慢來啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，上校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.39,0:11:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真的是夏亞！夏亞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢來，知道嗎？拉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什麼？退後些，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過是第一次見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何我會知道\N他就是夏亞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.57,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女孩\N好像是叫做拉拉的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你今年幾多歲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...十六歲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？真年輕呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也瞭解你面對敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心情可能會比較緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但至少也要說聲多謝呢！\N是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.03,0:11:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...沒錯！\N多謝你們的幫忙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了...我要走了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個少年到底做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定是聽過了\N紅色彗星的大名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.38,0:12:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道你是夏亞\N所以怕極了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實上，我們來了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是仍和以前一樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來再去想也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，就算再想\N也只是浪費時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.71,0:12:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等了你很久呢\N到底怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實上\N我只可以私人身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來幫各位忙的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆蘭...\N那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有艘私人的船...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打算用這個\N送你們出去港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有這裡的船\N就算是吉翁軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不會有膽來攻擊的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就可安心了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.03,0:13:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆蘭，到底為了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為了什麼\N難道妳還不明白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還要問我？米萊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你\N別再理我們的事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.41,0:13:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊...既然妳\N不肯離開母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最少，妳也接受我的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本就沒心幫我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你還說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣說，簡直是侮辱我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只是想我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.99,0:13:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認為你是個了不起的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，在我們最困難時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然不理我們\N還說什麼大話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...我的能力\N只能這樣而已...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那多謝了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢材！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉...？               你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，他確是誠心誠意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還不明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則他怎會冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.21,0:13:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說這裡是中立國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只要受到導彈的一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也會沒命的\N妳不明嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的為人也是...\N為什麼被這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一句聲也不抗辯呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用動手\N用口也一樣的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得憤怒\N便該打她那才是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以這樣粗魯的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.06,0:14:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？卡姆蘭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.93,0:14:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就認為這是對的\N是嗎？中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加中尉\N卡姆蘭檢察官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你的提議不變的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以幫我們這個忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！就起出港吧！中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過他們隔鄰\N有艘私家船啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然有這麼無聊的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆，出發了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該可以出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦好像改變了航線！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.72,0:15:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想向相反的方向逃走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要理侵犯領空的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻叫多姆出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他們在領空外作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.53,0:15:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可讓夏亞小看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.98,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你說過的條件\N不再作準了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要加收費用呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.85,0:15:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.99,0:15:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆蘭...\N現已到了領空的邊界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快返回去吧！   我知了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.66,0:15:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，吉翁的MS來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知了\N你就送到這裡吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...可以的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.67,0:15:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要盡力去到最遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和小孩子沒關係的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.35,0:16:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去主炮崗位了   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已接近\N衛星六號邊界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆蘭！         中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.49,0:16:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請退後吧！\N我現在要開火了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆蘭，很多謝你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我願意接受你的好意\N不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之是很多謝你\N卡姆蘭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回去吧！\N請代問候你父母！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美...米萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.98,0:16:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.55,0:16:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託，等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開大門\N鋼彈盡快出動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼加農，G戰機\N等候命令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.51,0:17:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地\N最大戰速，對空作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.69,0:17:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！多姆隊，攻擊開始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米加粒子炮，別射向離艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則會打中衛星六號的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.48,0:17:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.98,0:17:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了，怎辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.65,0:17:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開電視機吧！米萊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我來吧！\N等一會，凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別理會敵軍MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先阻止敵艦接近就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.48,0:18:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄準敵艦側面\N以導彈來防守！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.29,0:18:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒可能，怎會這樣的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎會預計到\N我們的動向...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看，巧合而已！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們集合\N一起攻擊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了\N我見到他們的行動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的看到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.11,0:19:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在領空外\N聯邦軍和吉翁軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙方正在交戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.32,0:19:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別拍白色基地\N快拍鋼彈吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.65,0:19:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看他怎樣和敵軍作戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅到底在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉，他們出來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好極，我知道了\N看著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在所見的\N正是一場戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.31,0:19:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍的母艦正在受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三艘的吉翁的攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們打得很激烈呢！\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要好好看清楚\N真實的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非如電影般好看的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果各位看完了這場戰事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.39,0:20:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後對國家的立場\N應加以討論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還收拾不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.88,0:20:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等...等一會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.39,0:20:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何阿姆羅今日的射擊\N會這樣准？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.69,0:20:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熱能快用完了！\N若不再用槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好用接近戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何會這樣？\N只有一艘戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.94,0:21:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然費這麼大的勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.71,0:21:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞在看著的\N全力進攻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.08,0:21:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們向著敵方母艦\N的腹部衝過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.53,0:21:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三艘吉翁\N已被聯邦軍消滅了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得白色的\NMS會贏的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.04,0:21:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔...電視還未\N映出來妳也知！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知的，若不這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.01,0:21:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校又怎會收留\N像我這樣的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉妳真聰明！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們衝過來\N表示他們已著急！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.36,0:21:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底它的要害在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.03,0:21:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它來了！         什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它已來到下面了！   什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.05,0:22:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.15,0:22:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯了，阿姆羅\N那就對了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.32,0:22:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是那零件的功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈充份利用它了！哈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.23,0:22:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球聯邦軍萬歲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.84,0:22:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以走了，回去吧！   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.51,0:22:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳一定生存下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 7...

